thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Sandra Antonio

author: Sandra Antonio
title: Sandra Antonio
text: Everything is good except it seems deserted and dark at night which is our only time to haul our stuff to our storage space.Also there's no accessibility as far as the equipment they promised to have like the wheels or bed for hauling our stuff from the vehicle to our storage space,and the office is closed.
